Building Dropbox Nautilus Extension From Source Tarball
--------------------------------------------------

You will need the following packages (or equivalant):

libnautilus-extension-dev
libnotify-dev

In the nautilus-dropbox dir just do:
$ ./configure
$ make
$ sudo make install

Building Dropbox Nautilus Extension From Mercurial
--------------------------------------------------

To compile you'll need the following packages (or equivalent):

gnome-common
libtool
autoconf
automake1.9
autotools-dev
libnautilus-extension-dev
libnotify-dev

In the nautilus-dropbox directory just do:

$ ./autogen.sh
$ make
$ sudo make install

should be good.

